### Hello World!

This is my first page on GitHub.io. I've never done this before, so I decided to just write a little blurb about myself.

I graduated from the University of British Columbia with a Bachelor's of Science, majoring in Computer Science: Software Engineering. I've currently work at [Safe Software](www.safe.com/about) in the city of Surrey. Surrey is a suburb of Vancouver and it's about 20-25 minute drive from the YVR airport.
